       000-PROC-SEC                SECTION.
      *
           INITIALIZE                  IDX-AREA
           INITIALIZE                  FLG-AREA
           INITIALIZE                  WRK-AREA
      *
      *    帳票名からＤＩＡかＭＯＮＰＥを設定する
           MOVE    SPACE               TO  WRK-DIA
           MOVE    ZERO                TO  FLG-OK
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX     FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL       IDX     >   50
               IF      MKPRT-DIA(IDX:1)    =   "."
                   MOVE    1               TO  FLG-OK
               ELSE
                   IF     (MKPRT-DIA(IDX:1)    NOT =   SPACE) AND
                          (FLG-OK              =   1        )
                       ADD     1               TO  IDY
                       MOVE    MKPRT-DIA(IDX:1)    TO  WRK-DIA (IDY:)
                   END-IF
               END-IF
               IF      MKPRT-DIA(IDX:1)    =   SPACE
                   MOVE    50              TO  IDX
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
           EVALUATE    WRK-DIA(1:3)
               WHEN    "dia"
      *            ｄａｉ
                   PERFORM 100-DIA-PRINT-SEC
               WHEN    "red"
      *            ＭＯＮＰＥ
                   PERFORM 200-MON-PRINT-SEC
               WHEN    OTHER
                   MOVE    99              TO  MKPRT-RC
           END-EVALUATE
      *
           .
       000-PROC-EXT.
      *
           EXIT    PROGRAM
